    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. You really have to see it in person to appreciate how pristine it is. It's perfect for someone who wants that brand-new feel without the brand-new price tag. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
