    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This beauty is in absolute mint condition and has been my pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied it since day one\u2014always garaged, meticulously detailed, and it still has that fresh new-car smell! It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner super happy. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
