    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E36 M3 that defines 'collector-grade.' This example features the S50 inline-six powerplant, showing impeccable compression across all cylinders and a completely silent Vanos system. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise ZF 5-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanically, it is flawless: the cooling system has been overhauled with an aluminum radiator, and the subframe has been inspected and reinforced for long-term chassis rigidity. It rides on a refreshed suspension with Bilstein B8 dampers and OEM bushings, maintaining the legendary M-Technic handling profile. All body panels retain original VIN tags, the paint depth is consistent throughout, and the interior Vaders show zero bolster wear or leather fatigue. A turnkey investment for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 43500.0,
